                        <li>You understand the risks associated with physical exercise and running</li>
                        <li>You agree to consult with a healthcare professional before beginning any new fitness routine</li>
                        <li>You will not hold Pacebeats liable for any injuries or health issues that may occur</li>
                        <li>You will use the app responsibly and within your physical limitations</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Music and Content Usage</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Pacebeats integrates with music streaming services to provide tempo-matched playlists. 
                        Users are responsible for having valid subscriptions to any third-party music services. 
                        We do not store or distribute copyrighted music content. All music is streamed through 
                        legitimate platforms in accordance with their respective terms of service.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Pacebeats is provided "as is" and "as available." We make no warranties about the accuracy 
                        of fitness data, continuous service availability, or results from using the app. 
                        We are not liable for any damages resulting from your use of the app, including but not limited to 
                        lost data, fitness injuries, or any other direct or indirect damages.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">8. Termination</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to Pacebeats at any time, 
                        without notice, for conduct that violates these Terms or is otherwise harmful to our service or other users. 
                        You may also terminate your account at any time by deleting the application and contacting us to remove your data.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">9. Governing Law</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        These Terms are governed by applicable local and international laws. Any disputes will be resolved 
                        through appropriate legal channels in accordance with the jurisdiction where Pacebeats operates.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">10. Contact Information</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        For questions or concerns regarding these Terms, please contact us:
                    </p>
                    <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-6">
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> pacebeatsspacebeats213@gmail.com</p>
                        <p><strong>Website:</strong> www.pacebeats.top</p>
                        <p><strong>Mobile App:</strong> Through the Pacebeats mobile application support section</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>

            <!-- Back to home button -->
            <div class="mt-8 text-center">
                <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 font-semibold">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Back to Home</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </main>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="bg-black border-t border-white/10 py-8 px-6 mt-12">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center text-gray-400 text-sm">
                <p>Â© 2025 Pacebeats. All rights reserved.</p>
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mt-4">
                    <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
                    <a href="/terms-and-conditions" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">Terms & Conditions</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Smooth scrolling */
    html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    
    /* Section spacing */
    section {
        scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    /* Link styling */
    a {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    /* Responsive adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
    }
</style>
